it.emarolab.scene_identification_tagging

Interface SITBase.OBJECT_PROPERTY

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    Enclosing interface:
    SITBase

    public static interface SITBase.OBJECT_PROPERTY
extends SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    The interface containing all the constants related to object properties.

    This interface is aimed to be a container for all the String constants used in the ontology for addressing object properties.
    Note that the implementation does not hard code the type of spatial relations. Those are obtained at run time by considering all the object properties that are used between two individual that belongs to SITBase.CLASS.PRIMITIVE or its sub classes.
